Food Fighters US - Season 2, Episode 5




Fighting Fire with Food

Ryan McKay, a firefighter and father of two from Atlanta, Georgia, believe his firehouse recipes will help him win $100,000 so his wife can open her own flower shop. She gave up everything for him to follow his dream of becoming a firefighter, and he wants to repay the favor.




Original Air Date: 30-Jul-2015
